cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper deals with the inference of Relax NG, a schema language for XML documents. This topic is closely related to data management, machine learning, and programming languages. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new subclass of regular expressions with interleaving, which is a topic in software engineering and programming languages. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages) are also likely sub-categories.
